Create a new CharacterEditor instance._

The "allowEmpty" parameter controls whether an empty String is_to be allowed in parsing, i.e. be interpreted as the null_value when {@link #setAsText(String) text is being converted}. If_false, an {@link IllegalArgumentException} will be thrown_at that time._@param allowEmpty if empty strings are to be allowed
